The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | Guess what makes Pitt laugh: his kids
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Guess what makes Pitt laugh: his kids
                            
	New York, Sept. 7 (PTI): What makes Brad Pitt laugh these days?        
	My kids, says the 44-year-old doting father.        
	Speaking of his eight-week-old twins with Angelina Jolie, Knox and Vivienne, the actor said they are great.        
	Everyone is healthy, said Pitt. No sleep though, Pitt was quoted as saying by the People.com.        
	Pitt and Jolie have six kids in total contributing to the giggles: Maddox, 7, Pax, 4, Zahara, 3, and Shiloh, 2 and the twins.                                                                                                                                                                           
